The '''''thakiz baw'kal''''', or the '''Downstorm''', was the [[Korun/Legends|Korunnai]] term for heavy winds that would blow across the surface of their home [[Planet/Legends|planet]], [[Haruun Kal/Legends|Haruun Kal]], during its brief [[Winter/Legends|winter]]. As the valleys of the planet were blanketed in a [[cloudsea]] of heavy toxic gases, any unfortunates in lower areas of the [[Korunnal Highland]] could be [[Death/Legends|killed]] by winds that blew these gases farther up.

